channel.title: Cooking
channel.description:
Well after 25 cooking I decided I'm gunna go for monks cook / sell
After 100 salmons and 1k tunas I got 50. Now I plan on going with lobs to 62.
On tip.it it estimated that I have to cook 1.9k lobs.
Now if anyone can estimate how many I need to buy because I plan on burning at least 1/3 of the load or so..
If I decide to tunas it will only take 2.6k including the burning.
